name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: New Tab Motivational Quotes & Image of Nature

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension which shows motivating quotes and random image on the new tab page.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A simple extension that loads a random quote and random image of nature to make your day a bit more bright.

There is no other data loaded or tracking being done when you you use this extension.
